Class NonResident

java.lang.Object

src.NonResident

Direct Known Subclasses:

public class NonResident
extends Student
This class, NonResident, extends Student as a subclass. Contains methods for checking what tuition should be due for the Student depending on credits enrolled and the toString() method.
Author:
Christian Osma, Liam Smith
